result.reason: CVE-2020-0765 is specific to Microsoft's Remote Desktop Connection Manager (RDCMan), not mRemoteNG — these are entirely different products and the CVE does not apply here
result.approach: No fix needed — CVE-2020-0765 targets Microsoft RDCMan which was deprecated by Microsoft rather than patched. mRemoteNG is a separate codebase unaffected by this CVE. Close as not-applicable.
